data.description: Two story Colonial in excellent move-in condition. First floor features all your gathering space which includes a spacious formal living and dining room, family room with gas log fireplace, and eat-in kitchen. Second floor features 4 bedrooms with master suite away from other bedrooms. Kitchen has lots of cabinets, newer SS appliances, a breakfast bar and bay window with sliders to large deck. New paint throughout. First floor laundry. New flooring in dining and family rooms. AC 2 years old. Roof/gutters under 3 years old. New fence surrounding a quarter+ acre. Harlem School district and lower taxes. Schedule your private showing today.
